overview: The user initiated a request to transform the aesthetic of their sleep
  questionnaire app, which they perceived as generic. The agent undertook a
  comprehensive review of the existing visual design, pinpointing areas such as
  the color palette, typography, spacing, and form elements that lacked a
  cohesive and engaging feel. The approach involved implementing a new, calming
  sleep-themed color palette, enhancing the main form layout with subtle
  decorative elements and a redesigned progress bar, and revitalizing the intro
  section with a hero component and interactive feature cards. Crucially, all 14
  individual questionnaire sections and core UI components like checkboxes,
  radio buttons, and sliders were updated to ensure a consistent and polished
  visual language. The agent systematically applied these changes, verified
  their appearance in the browser, and confirmed the absence of any linting
  errors, successfully transforming the app into a more professional and
  aesthetically pleasing sleep health tool.
